# Pest Multi Auth Guard Testing

## When to use

- Writing Pest tests for multiple auth guards (admin, member, vendor)
- Testing login/logout flows for separate user tables
- Testing middleware and route protection per guard
- Testing Filament panel access with different auth guards
- Testing Sanctum API tokens with multiple user types

## Keywords

`pest multi auth`, `auth guard test`, `multi login test`, `filament panel test`, `sanctum multi auth`, `guard middleware test`
